---
title: Shrimp & Sun-Dried Tomato Spaghetti with Fresh Parsley, Almonds & Parmesan
description: Does your love for pasta know no bounds? We’ve got the perfect recipe for any self-professed carb connoisseur. Al dente spaghetti, sun-dried tomatoes, juicy grape tomatoes, and fresh parsley come together in a combination that’s hearty, satisfying, and classically comforting–all in 20 minutes! Just add a sprinkle of Parmesan and crunchy toasted almonds over the top to take things... well, over the top!
